pera.it/tag/jaromir-weinberger/" rel="tag">Jaromír Weinberger</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/ludovit-ludha/" rel="tag">Ludovít Ludha</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marjorie-owens/" rel="tag">Marjorie Owens</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/michael-eder/" rel="tag">Michael Eder</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/mikhail-agrest/" rel="tag">Mikhail Agrest</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/pavol-kuban/" rel="tag">Pavol Kuban</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roberto-abbondanza/" rel="tag">Roberto Abbondanza</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/svanda-dudak/" rel="tag">Švanda dudák</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-massimo-di-palermo/" rel="tag">Teatro Massimo di Palermo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/timothy-oliver/" rel="tag">Timothy Oliver</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alfio Marletta, Anna Maria Chiuri, Axel Kohler, Jaromír Weinberger, Ludovít Ludha, Marjorie Owens, Michael Eder, Mikhail Agrest, Opera lirica, Pavol Kuban, Roberto Abbondanza, Švanda dudák, Teatro Massimo di Palermo, Timothy Oliver"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/3745e901d16aaca5157820d01520ca96" alt="" /> <img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3745e901d16aaca5157820d01520ca96?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Marco Crescimanno"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="ic